Name: Maurya Indians
Code: maur
Culture:
  - indian
Region:
  - asia
  - india
Emblem: session/portraits/emblems/emblem_mauryas.png
History: The Maurya Indians have excellent archers and a large number of
  champions, including war elephants, chariots, macemen, and Maiden Archers, who
  can swap weapons between sword and longbow. Their citizen infantry are low
  quality and cavalry are mediocre, but train quickly. Like the Chinese and
  Persians, the Indians have a +10% population cap bonus. Lastly, the Pillars of
  Ashoka boost nearby citizens.
